# Dependencies
node_modules/
# Worktree-local symlinks to main repo's node_modules (claude/elastic-pascal
# worktree pattern — see CLAUDE.md «Worktree Development Guide»). The temp
# suffix varies per worktree; pattern catches all variants. Symlinks point
# to local /Users paths that don't exist on CI / other machines.
.node_modules-*

